# Chatbot for iPhone Support
Virtual AI assistant that can help with iPhone support topics. 
It always retrieves semanthic context from the vector index.

Simple RAG pipeline using:
- LangChain
- Faiss
- Ollama or GPT-4 for chat model
- text-embedding-3-small for embeddings
- Selenium for scraping the documents
- Gradio

This requires OpenAI api key to use 'GPT-4' model (default), otherwise it uses GPT 3.5 turbo without api key. 